  "Question": "<p>When solving for the value, we know that <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_208\"><?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?> <math alttext=\"e^{\\pi i}=-1\" display=\"block\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <mrow> <msup> <mi>e</mi> <mrow> <mi>\u03c0</mi> <mo>\u2062</mo> <mi>i</mi> </mrow> </msup> <mo>=</mo> <mrow> <mo>-</mo> <mn>1</mn> </mrow> </mrow> </math></span> . I am confused as to what is the right answer when you evaluate this.I am getting two possible answers: <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_209\"><?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?> <math alttext=\"e^{3\\pi i/2}\" display=\"block\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <msup> <mi>e</mi> <mrow> <mrow> <mn>3</mn> <mo>\u2062</mo> <mi>\u03c0</mi> <mo>\u2062</mo> <mi>i</mi> </mrow> <mo>/</mo> <mn>2</mn> </mrow> </msup> </math></span> = <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_210\"><?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?> <math alttext=\"(e^{\\pi i})^{3/2}\" display=\"block\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <msup> <mrow> <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo> <msup> <mi>e</mi> <mrow> <mi>\u03c0</mi> <mo>\u2062</mo> <mi>i</mi> </mrow> </msup> <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>3</mn> <mo>/</mo> <mn>2</mn> </mrow> </msup> </math></span> so this could be <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_211\"><?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?> <math alttext=\"(\\sqrt{-1})^{3}=i^{3}=-i\" display=\"block\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <mrow> <msup> <mrow> <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo> <msqrt> <mrow> <mo>-</mo> <mn>1</mn> </mrow> </msqrt> <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo> </mrow> <mn>3</mn> </msup> <mo>=</mo> <msup> <mi>i</mi> <mn>3</mn> </msup> <mo>=</mo> <mrow> <mo>-</mo> <mi>i</mi> </mrow> </mrow> </math></span> or it could be <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_212\"><?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?> <math alttext=\"\\sqrt{(-1)^{3}}=\\sqrt{-1}=i\" display=\"block\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <mrow> <msqrt> <msup> <mrow> <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo> <mrow> <mo>-</mo> <mn>1</mn> </mrow> <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo> </mrow> <mn>3</mn> </msup> </msqrt> <mo>=</mo> <msqrt> <mrow> <mo>-</mo> <mn>1</mn> </mrow> </msqrt> <mo>=</mo> <mi>i</mi> </mrow> </math></span>. Which one is the correct answer, and where am I going wrong? Thanks.</p>",
